This well made leather armor is several centuries old, but due to its lasting enchantments, it is as ready for battle as ever.
Piecemeal or complete armors of this type offer basic protection, equivalent to hardened leather.
This cloak is made of several layers of thick fabric, allowing its wearer to slip by unnoticed...
Cloaks are simple cloth garments used to protect the wearer from bad weather and other hazards of the open road.
This well made short sword is several centuries old, but due to the lasting enchantments it bears, it appears as ready for battle as ever.
One of the first types of sword to come into existence, the short sword is a double-edged weapon about two feet long.  It is an economical weapon, and a favorite of archers and rogues.

value.10: Former Royal Magician Vangerdahast to King Azoun IV of Cormyr was once an accomplished adventurer of high fame. One reason he became popular in wizardly circles was his creation of the Adventurer's Robe. Mages have always struggled with the limitations placed on them by the ability to cast arcane magics. These robes give the mage an edge in surviving encounters with melee fighters by being able to absorb some damage from hits.
